Begin forwarded message:

From: David Ray <dray@cardkingdom.com>
Date: December 22, 2018 at 12:26:11 PM PST
To: Tim Cunningham <tim@cardkingdom.com>
Cc: Michael Zaborowski <mzaborowski@cardkingdom.com>
Subject: EDHrec Pricing

Hey Tim,
 
I’m not sure how EDHrec displays our prices or how often they update but it looks like a lot of them are displaying incorrectly. It looks like a lot of cards are displaying at prices from mid-late November. Sam pointed out a few discrepancies and I had him dig a bit deeper and we found a lot of incorrect prices on cards that haven’t been repriced in a while. Some examples are Taiga, Arcum Dagsson, Rings of Brighthearth, Toxin Sliver, and Niv-Mizzet, Parun. Arcum Dagsson is displaying at $16.99, which it hasn’t been priced at since 11/21. Taiga was last priced at 179.99 on 11/16."
